<h2 class="">4. Check your programming task results</h2>
<main>

  <% if @student.status_task_submitted? %>

    <h3 class="mt-0">Your submission is currently queued for review</h3>
    <p>
      We received your task submission on: <br>
      <span style="background-color: #dfe1ec"><%= @student.task_submissions.last.created_at.in_time_zone('Asia/Kolkata').to_s(:short_with_dayname) %></span>
    </p>
    <p>
      We review all submissions within 3 working days. We will email you after the review.
    </p>

    <p>And thanks for taking the time to work through the problem. We hope you enjoyed it.</p>

  <% end %>
</main>
